<br />
作者：<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tenth-lee" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5226483); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5226483&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1608635960" alt="Tenth Lee" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5226483)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tenth-lee" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5226483); return false;">Tenth Lee</a></span>
